       MERIT MODEL
      </strong>
     </p>
     <p>
      <strong>
       Rewarding Performance Advances UCI.
      </strong>
      The newly introduced pay for performance program for non-represented staff employees provides an opportunity to align individual employee objectives, milestones and targets with the university’s goals. Together we will advance UCI into our brilliant future.
     </p>
